description:
Beautifully Renovated 2 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Penthouse with your own Private Roofdeck! Unbeatable views! Enter into your spacious, open concept living/dining/kitchen perfect for entertaining! Gorgeous chef's kitchen featuring an oversized island, gas cooking, teak wood open shelving, full height pantry, Jennair Pro Style SS appliances and Silestone countertops w/ marble backsplash! Two generous size bedrooms both with their own en-suite baths & custom walk-in closets! Superior high-end finishes throughout including: smart home technology, radiant floor heating, smart locks, video intercom, LED lighting, nest thermostats, white oak flooring, custom laundry area, gas fireplace and built-in Sonos speakers in every room! Premier location! This condo truly has it all! Available July 1, July 15 or August 1.

Owner pays for cold water and sewer. Tenant responsible for heat, hot water, cooking gas, electricity. Non smoking unit. Street parking. Upfront costs = first months rent + 1 month security + 1 month broker fee = $15,000.00

otherFacts.value: Hot water not included in rent
